176
00:15:53,748 --> 00:15:55,208
I know you young people are always...

177
00:15:55,291 --> 00:15:57,960
jabbing yourselves with ink and needles.

178
00:15:58,336 --> 00:16:00,171
You're written on, aren't you?

179
00:16:00,254 --> 00:16:02,173
Not where you can see.

180
00:16:02,256 --> 00:16:03,549
Well.

181
00:16:03,716 --> 00:16:06,844
He's to be bathed daily, his linens changed.

182
00:16:07,261 --> 00:16:11,057
Don't bother with the housework.
I'm the only one that knows how.

183
00:16:12,517 --> 00:16:14,936
How long have you two lived here?

184
00:16:16,479 --> 00:16:17,855
Let's see.

185
00:16:18,481 --> 00:16:21,734
We came over from Savannah in "62.

186
00:16:22,568 --> 00:16:25,613
