189
00:16:31,703 --> 00:16:34,247
VIOLET: There they are. Martin and Grace.

190
00:16:34,872 --> 00:16:36,582
VIOLET: Charming people.

191
00:16:37,542 --> 00:16:40,837
But they fell on hard times, had to sell.

192
00:16:41,379 --> 00:16:43,089
You keep their picture?

193
00:16:43,172 --> 00:16:47,010
Yes. I like to pay my respects
to the memories of this house.

194
00:17:02,608 --> 00:17:04,402
All right. Come along now.

195
00:17:11,159 --> 00:17:12,994
This is the dining room.

196
00:17:13,077 --> 00:17:14,787
We only use about half of the rooms.

197
00:17:14,871 --> 00:17:17,248
The others are for Ben's antique business.

198
00:17:17,332 --> 00:17:20,043
