199
00:17:20,126 --> 00:17:22,128
Except for the attic.

200
00:17:22,295 --> 00:17:24,339
That has crystal and china.

201
00:17:24,422 --> 00:17:28,092
And I keep a very close account
on that, just so as you know.

202
00:17:31,304 --> 00:17:33,848
There are more than 30 rooms in all.

203
00:17:34,057 --> 00:17:37,643
In the old days, they made
a separate key for each room.

204
00:17:37,727 --> 00:17:40,897
For the owner, they made a skeleton key.

205
00:17:41,856 --> 00:17:43,900
This will open every door.

206
00:17:44,525 --> 00:17:46,194
This one is yours.

207
00:17:47,487 --> 00:17:48,905
I have mine.

208
00:17:50,365 --> 00:17:52,200
Now, the pantry's right out here.

209
00:17:52,283 --> 00:17:56,079
You know, we may have to ask you
to go into town now and then.

210
00:17:56,162 --> 00:17:58,081
Was there a mirror here once?

211
00:18:00,583 --> 00:18:03,294
I noticed in the bathrooms also
there are no mirrors.

212
00:18:03,378 --> 00:18:06,464
Child, when you get as worn-out
and wrinkled as we are...

213
00:18:06,547 --> 00:18:08,299
you don't need any reminding.

214
00:18:08,383 --> 00:18:10,510
If you want a small one
for your own purposes...

215
00:18:10,593 --> 00:18:11,678
that's fine with me.

216
00:18:11,761 --> 00:18:14,555
- What'd you do with them?
- Put them away.

217
00:18:20,311 --> 00:18:22,814
VIOLET: The boy tells me you don't smoke.

218
00:18:22,897 --> 00:18:25,983
I do smoke. I smoke a lot
and I enjoy it very much.

219
00:18:26,067 --> 00:18:27,485
I trust that won't be an issue.

220
00:18:27,568 --> 00:18:28,653
It won't be.

221
00:18:28,736 --> 00:18:31,239
Good. Then for the most part
just realize that...

222
00:18:31,322 --> 00:18:33,491
l'll live here as if you're not in residence.

223
00:18:33,574 --> 00:18:37,036
